<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>About Potty Partner</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
</head>
<body>
  {{> header}}

  <div class="container mt-4">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-12">
        <h1 class="text-center">About Potty Partner</h1>
        <p class="lead text-center">
          Potty Partner is your reliable companion for finding the best restrooms nearby. Whether you're traveling, exploring a new city, or just in need of a restroom, Potty Partner helps you locate clean and accessible restrooms in your vicinity.
        </p>
        <p>
          Our mission is to provide users with the most accurate and up-to-date information about restrooms, including ratings, reviews, and photos. With Potty Partner, you can:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Search for restrooms in your area</li>
          <li>View interactive maps with restroom locations</li>
          <li>Rate and review restrooms</li>
          <li>Upload photos of restrooms</li>
          <li>Save and favorite restrooms</li>
          <li>Comment on user posts and reviews</li>
          <li>Set your profile to public or private</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          We hope Potty Partner makes your restroom-finding experience easy and stress-free. Thank you for using our app!
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  {{> footer}}
</body>
</html>
